I have to move so fast.

346
00:36:41,691 --> 00:36:43,860
Carefully.

347
00:36:44,027 --> 00:36:47,489
- It's the same thing, Lillian.
- Henry, this is very important to me.

348
00:36:47,656 --> 00:36:49,282
