358
00:37:25,028 --> 00:37:27,280
Hey, man, it ain't up to me alone.

359
00:37:29,365 --> 00:37:31,868
- Purcell, can I see you a minute?
- Yeah, sure.

360
00:37:32,035 --> 00:37:33,995
Oh, I gotta-

361
00:37:35,539 --> 00:37:38,083
I love what you did
with old John Deach out there.

362
