442
00:44:02,021 --> 00:44:04,357
Felony number three.

443
00:44:04,524 --> 00:44:06,526
Habitual.

444
00:44:07,527 --> 00:44:11,281
- Judge gives you life for the toilet.
- Yeah, or give me the toilet for life.

445
00:44:12,115 --> 00:44:13,366
Same difference.

446
00:44:13,783 --> 00:44:17,370
